<div id="review_3901754850" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3901754850" />
    <a title="Mari" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1467875-mari"><img alt="Mari" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/f_50x66-6a03a5c12233c941481992b82eea8d23.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3901754850?book_show_action=true">Mar 21, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Mari" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Mari" href="/user/show/1467875-mari">Mari</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3901754850" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12404512202760800596">I received a free copy from Mr. Getze. He has a clever way of telling the story of how a surprise baby grows love and togetherness in the Soria family. Baby Noelle didn’t think she’d ever get the love she sought. Emily didn’t know what or how to act with her new little girl. Her family, especially her Mama loved Noelle right away. But with some drug use within her family, and a “best” friend so jealous and trying to sabotage little Noelle, it created so much trouble for the Soria’s. And then the</span>
  <span id="freeText12404512202760800596" style="display:none">I received a free copy from Mr. Getze. He has a clever way of telling the story of how a surprise baby grows love and togetherness in the Soria family. Baby Noelle didn’t think she’d ever get the love she sought. Emily didn’t know what or how to act with her new little girl. Her family, especially her Mama loved Noelle right away. But with some drug use within her family, and a “best” friend so jealous and trying to sabotage little Noelle, it created so much trouble for the Soria’s. And then there’s the same boyfriend they both liked...</span>
