        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3981887951" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8143724719617107978">This book was entertaining but I really did not like how adoption was depicted in the beginning as “throwing a baby away.” I found this a bit offensive. Most parents who give their children up for adoption do so to give them a chance at a better life than they themselves could give them.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


